FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774004767
OL,3,CKing dons sturdy shoes on trek to mark
OL,4,Claunch of coastal path and nature
OL,5,Creserve
OL,7,FThe 13 reserves declared so far,
OL,8,Fincluding the nature-rich chalklands
OL,9,Fof Seven Sisters, in Seaford now cover
OL,10,Fan area of 65 square miles, twice the
OL,11,Fsize of the city of Brighton.
OL,13,FOn his visit to the beauty spot on
OL,14,FThursday, Charles also trekked two
OL,15,Fkilometres to mark the launch of the
OL,16,Flongest managed coastal walking route
OL,17,Fin the world, the King Charles III
OL,18,FEngland Coast Path.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774004767
OL,3,CKing dons sturdy shoes on trek to mark
OL,4,Claunch of coastal path and nature
OL,5,Creserve
OL,7,FHe walked the path alongside passers-
OL,8,Fby wearing his lounge suit and brown
OL,9,Fbrogues, armed with a walking staff.
OL,11,FRambler Sharon Willmoore, 76, was out
OL,12,Fwalking with her friend when she said
OL,13,Fshe was "amazed" to see the King.
OL,15,FShe said: "Not what we were expecting
OL,16,Fat all, just out for a nice walk and
OL,17,Fsomeone said the King was along there."
OL,26,@uD@IOUuD@PO]wD@KOUyD@gO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
