OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774004767
OL,3,CKing dons sturdy shoes on trek to mark
OL,4,Claunch of coastal path and nature
OL,5,Creserve
OL,7,FAs Charles approached the white cliffs
OL,8,Flandmark, he said they were the ones
OL,9,F"I avoided hitting when I was in the
OL,10,FRoyal Navy".
OL,12,FThe King also spoke to a group of
OL,13,Fcyclists who said they were riding e-
OL,14,Fbikes, to which he joked: "Cheaters."
OL,16,FNatural England is officially
OL,17,Flaunching the path, which passes
OL,18,Fthrough the Seven Sisters nature
OL,19,Freserve, as the 2,700-mile route nears
OL,20,Fcompletion.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@KO]vD@[OUvD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
