FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774004767
OL,3,CKing dons sturdy shoes on trek to mark
OL,4,Claunch of coastal path and nature
OL,5,Creserve
OL,7,FOfficials behind the scheme estimate
OL,8,Fthe coast path, which has been nearly
OL,9,Ftwo decades in the making, would take
OL,10,Fa year to walk ` with weekends off.
OL,12,FPolly Martin, of National Trails UK,
OL,13,Fwho met the King on Thursday, said she
OL,14,Fis hoping the launch will raise
OL,15,Fawareness that the work that trails
OL,16,Fofficers do in "good weather, bad
OL,17,Fweather, is incredible".
OL,26,@xD@POUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
