PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774004767
OL,3,CKing dons sturdy shoes on trek to mark
OL,4,Claunch of coastal path and nature
OL,5,Creserve
OL,7,FShe said she sees "today as a
OL,8,Fcelebration" of all the work that has
OL,9,Fbeen done to make the path open and
OL,10,Fuseable.
OL,12,FMs Martin added: (We're) hoping the
OL,13,Fcoast path named after the King will
OL,14,Fmake people more aware of the
OL,15,Fimportance of national trails."
OL,26,@oD@SOUpD@LO]wD@_O]
