PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774004767
OL,3,CKing dons sturdy shoes on trek to mark
OL,4,Claunch of coastal path and nature
OL,5,Creserve
OL,7,FOn the Sussex coast, the path passes
OL,8,Fover the Seven Sisters cliffs, which
OL,9,Fhave been inspiration for the poet
OL,10,FRudyard Kipling, a backdrop to films
OL,11,Fincluding Atonement, Harry Potter And
OL,12,FThe Goblet Of Fire and Wicked, and are
OL,13,Fthe site of the new 1,500-hectare
OL,14,F(3,700-acre) national nature reserve.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
