FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774004767
OL,3,CKing dons sturdy shoes on trek to mark
OL,4,Claunch of coastal path and nature
OL,5,Creserve
OL,7,FThe reserve, stretching across the
OL,8,Fcliffs and the Cuckmere River which
OL,9,Fcuts through them, sits within the
OL,10,FSouth Downs National Park and is home
OL,11,Fto globally rare habitats, including
OL,12,Fchalk grasslands, heath and floodplain
OL,13,Fmeadows.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
